%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hardik%20Pandya%20likely%20to%20miss%20Afghanistan%20T20I%20series%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703664801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106316269%2Cimgsize-52768.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fhardik-pandya-likely-to-miss-afghanistan-t20i-series-will-be-fit-before-ipl-sources%2Farticleshow%2F106316276.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20all-rounder%20Hardik%20Pandya%20is%20likely%20to%20miss%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20Afghanistan%20and%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Pandya%20sustained%20an%20ankle%20injury%20during%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20has%20been%20out%20of%20action%20since%20then.%20He%20has%20not%20played%20international%20cricket%20and%20missed%20the%20T20I%20series%20against%20Australia%20and%20the%20tour%20to%20South%20Africa.%20Pandya%20recently%20joined%20Mumbai%20Indians%20as%20the%20new%20skipper%2C%20taking%20over%20from%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20who%20has%20led%20the%20franchise%20to%20five%20IPL%20title%20wins.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ANI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Chicken%20loot'%20on%20Agra-Delhi%20highway%3B%20video%20goes%20viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703664452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106316070%2Cimgsize-19172.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fagra%2Fchicken-loot-on-agra-delhi-highway-after-lorry-carrying-birds-crashes-in-12-vehicle-pile-up%2Farticleshow%2F106316040.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chaos%20ensued%20on%20Agra-Delhi%20Highway%20when%20a%20lorry%20transporting%20chickens%20met%20with%20an%20accident.%20Onlookers%20and%20commuters%20started%20looting%20the%20birds%20from%20the%20vehicle.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%