on%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESukesh%20Chandrashekar%20has%20sought%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20the%20case%20and%20alleged%20that%20his%20voice%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bcloned%26quot%3B%20using%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20and%20%26quot%3Bchats%20have%20been%20created%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20threatened%20to%20expose%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conman%20made%20several%20allegations%20against%20the%20actor%20in%20a%20public%20letter%20and%20sought%20to%20probe%20%26quot%3Bhow%20crores%20were%20transferred%20by%20him%20to%20a%20social%20media%20management%20firm%20to%20purchase%20fake%20followers%2C%20around%2020%20million%2C%20for%20her%20Instagram%20account%26quot%3B.%20He%20claimed%20that%20Ms%20Fernandez%20wanted%20to%20compete%20with%20actor%20Katrina%20Kaif's%20following%20on%20Instagram%20and%20sought%20to%20probe%20the%20chats%20between%20him%20and%20her%20over%20the%20same.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConman%20said%20he%20had%20approached%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20over%20the%20messages%20on%20WhatsApp%20and%20Webex%20in%20August%20for%20an%20investigation%20and%20the%20court%20ordered%20a%20detailed%20investigation%20in%20which%20it%20was%20concluded%20that%20no%20messages%20were%20sent%20by%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Fernandes%20has%20been%20questioned%20multiple%20times%20by%20probe%20agencies%20in%20the%20laundering%20case%20against%20the%20conman.%20The%20actor%20has%20filed%20a%20petition%20before%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20to%20quash%20the%20case%20and%20a%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20against%20her.%20She%20has%20said%20she%20is%20%26quot%3Ban%20innocent%20victim%26quot%3B%20of%20Chandrashekar's%20%26quot%3Bmaliciously%20targeted%20attack%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20opposed%20the%20petition%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20actor%20has%20not%20refuted%20the%20allegations%20that%20she%20received%20gifts%20worth%20Rs%207.12%20crore%20from%20Chandrashekar%20and%