%20Hotel%20Bathtub%20After%20Win%2C%20Stripped%20Of%20Title%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20of%20Chinese%20chess%20is%20in%20uproar%20over%20rumours%20of%20cheating%20and%20a%20bad%20behaviour%20scandal%20that%20saw%20the%20national%20champion%20stripped%20of%20his%20title%20Monday%20after%20a%20victory%20celebration%20ended%20with%20him%20defecating%20in%20a%20hotel%20bathtub.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXiangqi%2C%20or%20Chinese%20chess%2C%20has%20been%20hugely%20popular%20for%20hundreds%20of%20years%20across%20Asia%20--%20and%2048-year-old%20Yan%20Chenglong%20beat%20dozens%20of%20contenders%20last%20week%20to%20win%20the%20title%20of%20%26quot%3BXiangqi%20King%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20national%20tournament%20hosted%20by%20the%20Chinese%20Xiangqi%20Association%20(CXA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20joy%20was%20short-lived%2C%20with%20the%20CXA%20on%20Monday%20announcing%20that%20Yan%20would%20have%20his%20title%20revoked%20and%20prize%20money%20confiscated%20after%20had%20been%20caught%20%26quot%3Bdisrupting%20public%20order%26quot%3B%20and%20displaying%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20bad%20character%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20was%20also%20forced%20to%20address%20rumours%20circulating%20online%20that%20Yan%20had%20cheated%20during%20the%20competition%20by%20using%20anal%20beads%20equipped%20with%20wireless%20transmitters%20to%20send%20and%20receive%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYan%20allegedly%20clenched%20and%20unclenched%20rhythmically%20to%20communicate%20information%20about%20the%20chess%20board%20via%20code%20to%20a%20computer%2C%20which%20then%20sent%20back%20instructions%20on%20what%20moves%20to%20make%20in%20the%20form%20of%20vibrations%2C%20according%20to%20reports%20circulating%20on%20the%20Chinese%20social%20site%20Weibo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20it%20is%20currently%20impossible%20to%20prove%20that%20Yan%20engaged%20in%20cheating%20via%20'anal%20beads'%20as%20speculated%20on%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CXA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20was%20still%20stripped%20of%20his%20title%20and%20banned%20from%20playing%20for%20a%20year%20after%20his%20celebrations%20went%20wayward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYan%20consumed%20alcohol%20with%20others%20in%20his%20room%20on%20the%20night%20of%20the%2017th%2C%20and%20then%20he%20defecated%20in%20the%20bathtub%20of%20the%20room%20he%20was%20staying%20in%20on%20the%2018th%2C%20in%20an%20act%20that%20damaged%20hotel%20property%2C%20violated%20public%20order%20and%20good%20morals%2C%20had%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20the%20competition%20and%20the%20event%20of%20Xiangqi%2C%20and%20was%20of%20extremely%20bad%20character%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20association%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20amount%20of%20prize%20money%20Yan%20was%20forfeiting%2C%20but%20Xiangqi%20tournaments%20often%20promise%20winners%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20yuan%20(thousands%20of%20dollars).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CXA%20had%20published%20a%20social%20media%20post%20last%20week%20congratulating%20Yan%20and%20other%20players%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Bspectacularly%20heated%20high-level%20gameplay%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20included%20a%20photo%20of%20Yan%20on%20stage%2C%20flanked%20by%20two%20runners%20up%2C%20proudly%20holding%20up%20his%20prize%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703663700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fr8ccknv8_chinese-chess-getty-image_625x300_27_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-chess-champ-yan-chenglong-defecates-in-hotel-bathtub-after-win-stripped-of-title-4750525%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%20of%20Chinese