er%20the%20World%20Cup%20final%20against%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-match%20T20I%20series%20against%20Afghanistan%20will%20be%20India's%20final%20international%20assignment%2C%20taking%20place%20from%20January%2011-17%2C%20before%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20which%20will%20take%20place%20in%20June%20at%20West%20Indies%2FUSA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20this%20year%2C%20Pandya%20moved%20from%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%20to%20his%20former%20franchise%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20after%20a%20trade%20between%20both%20franchises.%20The%20all-rounder%20spent%20two%20momentous%20years%20with%20GT%2C%20spearheading%20their%20campaign%20with%20aplomb.%20In%20GT's%20debut%20season%20in%202022%2C%20Hardik%20ensured%20a%20fairytale%20start%2C%20with%20the%20team%20lifting%20the%20coveted%20trophy%2C%20while%20they%20finished%20runners-up%20in%20their%20second%20season%20after%20a%20last-ball%20defeat%20in%20a%20thrilling%20final%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20has%20big%20shoes%20to%20fill%20as%20the%20new%20skipper%20of%20MI%2C%20as%20Rohit%20has%20led%20the%20franchise%20to%20five%20IPL%20title%20wins.%20He%20was%20announced%20as%20the%20new%20skipper%20of%20MI%20days%20after%20his%20trade%20to%20the%20franchise%20which%20put%20him%20on%20the%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2031%20matches%20for%20GT%20from%202022-23%2C%20Pandya%20scored%20833%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2037.86%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20133%2C%20with%20six%20half-centuries%20and%20a%20best%20score%20of%2087*.%20He%20also%20had%2011%20wickets%20for%20the%20team%2C%20with%20the%20best%20figures%20of%203%2F17.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20also%20played%2092%20matches%20for%20MI%20from%202015-2021%2C%20scoring%201%2C476%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2027.33%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20153%2C%20with%20four%20half-centuries%20and%20best%20score%20of%2091.%20He%20also%20took%2042%20wickets%20for%20the%20team%2C%20with%20the%20best%20bowling%20figures%20of%203%2F20.%20Pandya%20has%20won%20five%20IPL%20trophies%2C%20four%20with%20MI%20(2015%2C%202017%2C%202019%2C%202020)%20and%20GT%20(2022).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703663220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fvqj49quo_hardik-pandya_625x300_28_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-suffer-hardik-pandya-blow-for-afghanistan-t20is-all-rounder-likely-to-miss-series-report-4750469%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20three-match%20T20I%20series%20against%20Afghanistan%20will%20be%20India's%20final%20international%20assignment%2C%20taking%20place%20from%20January%2011-17%2C%20before%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20which%20will%20take%20place%20in%20June%20at%20West%20Indies%2FUSA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-suffer-hardik-pandya-blow-for-afghanistan-t20is-all-rounder-likely-to-miss-series-report-4750469%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-suffer-hardik-pandya-blow-for-afghanistan-t20is-all-rounder-likely-to-miss-series-report-4750469%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Findia-suffer-hardik-pandya-blow-for-afghanistan-t20is-all-rounder-likely-to-miss-series-report-4750469%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JN.1%20variant%20Covid%20cases%20cross%20100%3A%20Symptoms%2C%20preventive%20measures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703663216000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106315456%2Cimgsize-1076092.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fhealth-fitness%2Fhealth-news%2Fjn-1-variant-covid-cases-cross-100-mark-highest-from-gujarat-symptoms-to-note-preventive-measures-to-know%2Farticleshow%2F106315498.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20total%20of%20109%20COVID%20cases%20due%20to%20the%20JN.1%20subvariant%20have%20been%20detected%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%2036%20cases%20from%20Gujarat%2C%2034%20from%20Karnataka%2C%2014%20from%20Goa%2C%209%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%206%20from%20Kerala%2C%204%20each%20from%20Rajasthan%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%202%20from%20Telangana%2C%20according%20to%20official%20sources.%20Most%20of%20the%20patients%20are%20currently%20in%20home%20isolation.%20There%20is%20no%20immediate%20concern%20as%2092%25%20of%20those%20infected%20are%20opting%20for%20home-based%20treatment%2C%20indicating%20a%20mild%20illness.%20There%20is%20no%20increase%20in%20hospitalization%20rates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20In%20Parliament%2C%20NDA%20May%20Well%20Be%20'No%20Data%20Available'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EParliamentary%20questions%20rarely%20make%20the%20headlines.%20However%2C%20questions%20raised%20and%20answered%20in%20parliament%20are%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20information.%20In%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20Question%20Hour%20has%20been%20a%20good%20opportunity%20for%20members%20in%20the%20opposition%20to%20expose%20the%20shallowness%20of%20this%20government%20and%20its%20disdain%20for%20solid%20data.%20From%20the%20hundreds%20of%20questions%20asked%20by%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20to%20this%20government%20during%20the%20'strangulated'%20winter%20session%20of%20parliament%2C%20this%20columnist%20has%20chosen%20just%20seven%20questions%20to%20make%20the%20point%20that%20the%20NDA%20(National%20Democratic%20Alliance)%20could%20very%20well%20stand%20for%20No%20Data%20Available%20(NDA)!%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Ministry%20of%20Social%20Justice%20and%20Empowerment%20(Manual%20Scavenging)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha's%20Aparupa%20Poddar's%20(Trinamool%20Congress)%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha's%20Md.%20Nadimul%20Haque%20(Trinamool)%20asked%20questions%20regarding%20data%20on%20manhole%20cleaning%20robots%20and%20deaths%20due%20to%20cleaning%20septic%20tanks.%20Conveniently%2C%20the%20government%20claimed%20the%20absence%20of%20centralised%20maintenance%20for%20this%20information.%20This%20is%20despite%20the%20Finance%20Minister's%20explicit%20mention%20of%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20manual%20scavenging%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget%202023.%20If%20only%20words%20could%20provide%20relief%20to%20communities%20in%20India%20that%20have%20experienced%20the%20highest%20indignities%20of%20caste%20for%20over%20a%20millennium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Ministry%20of%20Corporate%20Affairs%20(Chinese%20Companies%20in%20India)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20to%20Shyam%20Yadav%20Singh's%20(BSP)%20question%20on%20Chinese%20companies%20operating%20in%20India%20in%20the%20space%20of%20providing%20loans%20through%20apps%20was%20bewildering.%20The%20answer%20revealed%20that%2053%20Chinese%20companies%20have%20established%20a%20place%20of%20business%20in%20India.%20But%20the%20government%20has%20'no%20data%20available'%20on%20the%20details%20of%20their%20business%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20(Displacement%20of%20Tribal%20Students%20in%20Manipur)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Lorho%20S%20Pfoze's%20(NPF)%20inquiry%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20on%20tribal%20students%20displaced%20in%20the%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20sidestepped%20the%20crucial%20issue%20of%20rehabilitation.%20Even%20after%20seven%20months%20of%20Manipur%20unrest%2C%20there%20is%20an%20absence%20of%20any%20concrete%20government%20effort%20to%20collect%20data%20on%20the%20students%20affected%20by%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%2C%20clearly%20demonstrating%20a%20disregard%20for%20their%20welfare.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20in%202016%20was%20lauded%20for%20his%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20my%20conviction%20to%20bring%20the%20North-East%20at%20par%20with%20other%20developed%20regions%20of%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%20These%20words%20seem%20hollow%20when%20the%20students%2C%20perhaps%20the%20most%20affected%20by%20the%20ethnic%20strife%2C%20are%20the%20least%20of%20the%20government's%20priorities.%20The%20ministry%20responded%20with%20a%20plan%20for%20online%20education%20for%20students%20missing%20out%20on%20crucial%20years%20of%20their%20development.%20Internet%20shutdowns%2C%20gentlemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20(Loan%20Recovery)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Venkatesan%20(CPI-M))%20asked%20a%20pointed%20question%20on%20the%20quantum%20of%20loans%20written%20off%20and%20the%20corresponding%20debt%20recovery%20from%20bad%20loans%20spanning%20the%20financial%20years%202014-15%20to%202022-23.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%20that%20public%20sector%20banks%20have%20written%20off%20a%20colossal%20amount%20of%20Rs%2010.4%20lakh%20crore%20in%20loans%20while%20only%20managing%20to%20recover%20a%20mere%20Rs%201.6%20lakh%20crore%20from%20these%20written-off%20loans.%20This%20substantial%20loss%20of%20public%20funds%20demands%20scrutiny%20and%20fuels%20concerns%20about%20serious%20setbacks%20to%20the%20exchequer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Ministry%20of%20Personnel%2C%20Public%20Grievances%20and%20Pensions%20(Pending%20RTI%20Appeals)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAD%20Singh%20(RJD)%20asked%20a%20question%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20appeals%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20pending%20with%20the%20Central%20Information%20Commission%20and%20State%20Information%20Commission.%20The%20ministry%20robotically%20replied%20that%20the%20pendency%20has%20drastically%20reduced%20and%20the%20disposal%20rate%20increased.%20Ironically%2C%20no%20information%20was%20provided%20to%20substantiate%20these%20claims.%20No%20such%20attempt%20was%20even%20made%20to%20provide%20an%20answer%20about%20the%20states%2C%20and%20a%20dry%20%26quot%3Bthis%20information%20is%20with%20the%20state%20governments%26quot%3B%20was%20received%20in%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Ministry%20of%20Railways%20(Kavach%20System%20in%20Indian%20Railways)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%202023%20having%20been%20a%20torrid%20year%20for%20the%20Indian%20Railways%2C%20with%20devastating%20accidents%20like%20the%20ones%20in%20Balasore%2C%20Buxar%20and%20Vishakhapatnam%2C%20questions%20about%20the%20Kavach%20safety%20system%20in%20trains%20were%20met%20with%20an%20unsatisfactory%20response.%20The%20pertinent%20question%20was%20asked%20by%20Dhiraj%20Prasad%20Sahu%20(Congress)%2C%20KRN%20Rajeshkumar%20(DMK)%2C%20%C2%A0Digvijaya%20Singh%20(Congress)%20and%20Dr.%20Amee%20Yajnik%20(Congress)%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20%C2%A0The%20answer%20revealed%20that%20the%20system%20has%20only%20been%20deployed%20in%20the%20South%20Central%20Railway%20zone.%20The%20government%20didn't%20think%20it%20necessary%20to%20provide%20any%20insight%2C%20plan%2C%20or%20justification%20as%20to%20why%20the%20other%20zones%20are%20left%20without%20adequate%20safety%20mechanisms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Ministry%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20Food%20and%20Public%20Distribution%20(Cancellation%20of%20Ration%20Cards)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha%20MP%20Deepak%20Adhikari%20(Trinamool%20Congress)%20asked%20a%20question%20about%20the%20deletion%20and%20cancellation%20of%20fake%20ration%20cards%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20The%20data%20provided%20revealed%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20together%20accounted%20for%20a%20whopping%2027%20lakh%20cards%2C%20whereas%20West%20Bengal%20only%20had%206%20lakh%20cards%20cancelled.%20One%20is%20forced%20to%20think-%20why%20were%20so%20many%20fake%20cards%20required%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPostscript%3A%20For%20over%2060%20years%2C%20Question%20Hour%20was%20taken%20up%20at%2011%20am%2C%20followed%20by%20Zero%20Hour%20at%2012%20noon%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Question%20Hour%20would%20often%20be%20disrupted%20due%20to%20MPs%20wanting%20to%20raise%20crucial%20issues%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20day.%20In%202014%2C%20former%20Chairman%20Hamid%20Ansari%20flipped%20the%20timings%20and%20now%20Zero%20Hour%20starts%20at%2011%20am%2C%20followed%20by%20Question%20Hour%20at%2012%20noon.%20A%20noteworthy%20reform%20by%20a%20presiding%20officer.%20(Reform%20and%20presiding%20officers.%20Let's%20not%20say%20a%20word%20more!)%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20MP%2C%20leads%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703662800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fovml5cm8_new-parliament_625x300_20_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-parliament-nda-may-well-be-no-data-available-4750430%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parliamentary%20questions%20rarely%20make%20the%20headlines.%20However%2C%20questions%20raised%20and%20answered%20in%20parliament%20are%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20information.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-parliament-nda-may-well-be-no-data-available-4750430%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20crackdown%20on%20tech%20companies%20isn't%20over%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20going%20back%20to%20pre-2020's%20'business-as-usual%2C'%20says%20China%20Beige%20Book%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Xi%20Jinping%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64147da75f4f5400191a1309%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221359%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EXi%20Jinping%20makes%20a%20public%20pledge%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Constitution%20at%20the%20Great%20Hall%20of%20the%20People%20in%20Beijing%20on%20March%2010%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EXie%20Huanchi%2FXinhua%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20tech%20crackdown%20isn't%20over%2C%C2%A0Shehzad%20Qazi%2C%20the%20international%20managing%20director%20of%20China%20Beige%20Book%2C%20told%20Yahoo%20Finance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20started%20a%20regulatory%20crackdown%20against%20the%20tech%20sector%20in%20late%202020%20and%20has%20signaled%20it's%20winding%20down.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20investors%20were%20caught%20off%20guard%20by%20a%20slate%20of%20new%20draft%20rules%20for%20the%20online%20games%20sector%20last%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20tech%20crackdown%20isn't%20quite%20over%2C%20said%20an%20expert%20on%20Tuesday%20who%20weighed%20on%20Beijing's%20latest%20moves%20against%20the%20video%20games%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20end%20to%20a%20range%20of%20China%20watchers%20getting%20up%20on%20TV%20channels%20and%20saying%20things%20like%20Beijing%20is%20becoming%20pragmatic%2C%20the%20tech%20crackdown%20is%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Shehzad%20Qazi%2C%20the%20international%20managing%20director%20of%20China%20Beige%20Book%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fvideo%2Fera-lax-rules-tech-companies-220737195.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYahoo%20Finance.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bover%20the%20last%20two%20years%20they've%20been%20proven%20wrong%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Qazi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20started%20a%20regulatory%20crackdown%20against%20the%20tech%20sector%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-china-tech-crackdown-from-algorithms-to-crypto-mining-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elate%202020.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Chinese%20authorities%20signaled%20the%20crackdown%20was%20ending%20%E2%80%94%20but%20a%20sudden%20slate%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nppa.gov.cn%2Fxxfb%2Ftzgs%2F202312%2Ft20231221_823187.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enew%20draft%20rules%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20Friday%20targeting%20the%20online%20games%20sector%20spooked%20investors%20who%20feared%20a%20renewed%2C%20harsh%20crackdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fears%20sent%20the%20market%20into%20a%20tailspin%2C%20with%20related%20stocks%20losing%20over%20%2480%20billion%20in%20a%20day.%20The%20authority%20that%20released%20the%20new%20draft%20rules%20went%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-damage-control-crackdown-online-games-tencent-netease-selloff-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edamage%20control%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20worst%20of%20the%20crackdown%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20Beijing's%20scrutiny%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fjack-ma-alibaba-ant-financial-criticism-beijing-valuation-net-worth-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20giant%20Alibaba%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20may%20be%20over%2C%20Qazi%20told%20Yahoo%20Finance%20that%20the%20paradigm%20has%20already%20shifted.%20So%20investors%20probably%20shouldn't%20count%20on%20going%20back%20to%20pre-2020%20business-as-usual%20mode%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20the%20era%20of%20lax%20rules%20or%20no%20rules%20around%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20generally%20speaking%20in%20China%2C%20are%20completely%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20Qazi%20told%20the%20media%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20also%20certain%20is%20that%20the%20operating%20environment%20in%20China%20has%20become%20more%20uncertain%20and%20unpredictable%2C%20said%20Qazi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20investors%20shouldn't%20count%20on%20predictability%20for%20the%20sector%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20impossible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20unless%20you're%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20the%20top%20leadership%20in%20the%20Communist%20Party%2C%20you%20really%2C%20quite%20frankly%20won't%20know%20what's%20coming%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-tech-crackdown-not-over-regulations-beige-book-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703662767000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658bc0101c5c7b8c9a0c25d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-tech-crackdown-not-over-regulations-beige-book-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20started%20a%20regulatory%20crackdown%20against%20the%20tech%20sector%20in%20late%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-economy-tech-crackdown-not-over-regulations-beige-book-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Intel%20partners%20with%20Israel%20to%20invest%20%2425%20bn%20in%20new%20manufacturing%20facility%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703662549000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2018-01%2F26%2Ffull%2F1516980301-0667.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fintel-partners-with-israel-to-invest-25-bn-in-new-manufacturing-facility-123122700311_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20factory%20is%20expected%20to%20begin%20operating%20in%202028.%20Intel%20will%20operate%20it%20at%20least%20till%202035%22%2C%22author%