2F12%2F27%2Fchina%2Fchina-warns-military-fans-photos-online-intl-hnk-ml%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20State%20Security%20as%20saying%20on%20WeChat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20a%20focus%20on%20military%20airports%2C%20ports%2C%20national%20defence%20and%20military%20industrial%20units%2C%20they%20drove%20to%20or%20took%20ferries%20or%20planes%20that%20pass%20by%20designated%20routes%2C%20and%20clandestinely%20photographed%20with%20telephoto%20lenses%20or%20drones%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20civilian%20spy%20agency%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%20time%20or%20occasional%20offenders%20may%20receive%20only%20a%20warning%20but%20repeat%20violators%20rule%20could%20be%20imprisoned%20for%20up%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20the%20agency%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20particularly%20highlighted%20that%20these%20images%20could%20potentially%20expose%20technical%20details%20and%20progress%20in%20military%20equipment%2C%20such%20as%20aircraft%20carriers%2C%20and%20be%20used%20by%20%26quot%3Bhostile%20foreign%20forces%26quot%3B%20to%20analyse%20combat%20effectiveness%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3246167%2Fnational-security-china-warns-military-buffs-not-photograph-classified-equipment%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20impact%20defence%20planning%20by%20revealing%20the%20location%20of%20deployment%20and%20the%20type%20of%20military%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20offenders%20who%20used%20professional%20equipment%20such%20as%20telephoto%20lenses%20and%20drones%20to%20secretly%20photograph%20military%20equipment%20were%20punished%2C%20the%20SCMP%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20one%20such%20person%20was%20sentenced%20to%20prison%20on%20charges%20of%20illegally%20obtaining%20state%20secrets%20after%20secretly%20filming%20the%20Fujian%20a