A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Telangana%20government%20on%20Tuesday%20launched%20a%20scheme%20for%20citizens%20to%20pay%20pending%20challans%20at%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20original%20value.%20Under%20the%20scheme%2C%20the%20state%20government%20is%20offering%2060-90%20per%20cent%20discount%20on%20the%20traffic%20challan%20amount.%20The%20one-time%20settlement%20scheme%20will%20remain%20open%20from%20December%2026%20to%20January%2010.%20However%2C%20several%20users%20complained%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20get%20the%20declared%20discount%20and%20shared%20several%20posts%20on%20X%20tagging%20Hyderabad%20Police.%20A%20government%20order%20(GO)%20was%20soon%20issued%20to%20clarify%20all%20doubts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20government%20order%2C%2090%20per%20cent%20discount%20will%20be%20offered%20to%20owners%20of%20push%20carts.%20They%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20only%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20challan%20amount%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%2090%20per%20cent%20will%20be%20waived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20discount%20is%20offered%20to%20RTC%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20the%20orders%20the%20percentage%20of%20challans%20are%20divided%20according%20to%20the%20category%20of%20the%20vehicle.%20The%20push%20carts%20and%20TSRTC%20buses%20are%20to%20pay%2010%25%20of%20the%20challan%20amount%20with%20a%20waiver%20of%2090%25.%20Meanwhile%2C%202%20and%203%20wheeler%20are%20to%20pay%2020%25%20of%20the%20total%20challan%20amount%20with%20a%20waiver%20of%2080%25.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJEYnHZygL4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJEYnHZygL4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Telangana%20Gig%20and%20Platform%20Workers%20Union%20(%40TGPWU)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTGPWU%2Fstatus%2F1739613056177713247%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20two-wheelers%20and%20three-wheelers%2C%20the%20government%20has%20waived%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20challan%20amount.%20The%20discount%20in%20case%20of%20cars%20and%20other%20light%20motor%20vehicles%20and%20trucks%20and%20other%20heavy%20motor%20vehicles%20is%2060%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20was%20part%20of%20the%20election%20manifesto%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20implemented%20it%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20vehicle%20owners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20pay%20the%20amount%2C%20the%20government%20order%20has%20asked%20vehicle%20owners%20to%20visit%20the%20Telangana%20traffic%20e-challan%20website%2C%20check%20pending%20challan%20against%20their%20vehicles%20and%20pay%20the%20discounted%20amount%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20say%20about%20two%20crore%20traffic%20challans%20are%20pending%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Centre%20had%20informed%20Parliament%20that%20more%20than%204.73%20crore%20challans%20worth%20Rs%207%2C563.60%20crore%20were%20issued%20for%20traffic%20violations%20across%20the%20country%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Minister%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20had%20further%20said%20that%20the%20authorities%20had%20issued%20more%20than%204.21%20crore%20challans%20worth%20Rs%205%2C318.70%20crore%20for%20traffic%20violations%20across%20the%20country%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%20provided%20by%20the%20minister%2C%20Karnataka%20(87%2C48%2C963)%20has%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20registered%20vehicles%20(greater%20than%20or%20equal%20to%2015%20years)%2C%20followed%20by%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(74%2C91%2C584)%20and%20Delhi%20(57%2C85%2C609).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703661180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Frro154tg_traffic-generic_625x300_13_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A