issues%20have%20delayed%20shipments%20of%20Russian%20Sokol%20crude%20oil%20to%20Indian%20Oil%20Corp.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIndia%20prefers%20rupee%20payments%2C%20but%20Russia%20is%20unwilling%20to%20use%20the%20currency.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnd%20the%20Rosneft%20unit%20selling%20the%20oil%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20open%20a%20bank%20account%20in%20the%20UAE%20to%20accept%20dirham%20payments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMoscow%20has%20been%20on%20a%20drive%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdedollarization-russia-putin-trade-local-national-currencies-yuan-ruble-sco-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereplace%20the%20use%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20international%20trade%2C%20but%20there%20are%20barrels%20of%20Russian%20oil%20stuck%20at%20sea%20due%20to%20issues%20with%20paying%20in%20alternative%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShipments%20of%20Russian%20Sokol%20grade%20crude%20oil%20to%20state-owned%20Indian%20Oil%20Corp%2C%20or%20IOC%2C%20have%20been%20delayed%20by%20payment%20issues%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fenergy%2Fpayment-woes-delay-supply-russian-sokol-oil-india-sources-2023-12-26%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20citing%20two%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20The%20seller%20is%20the%20state-owned%20Russian%20oil%20company%20Rosneft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20arose%20because%20the%20Rosneft%20unit%20selling%20the%20oil%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20open%20a%20bank%20account%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20to%20receive%20payments%20in%20the%20UAE%20dirham%2C%20per%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20delayed%20six%20cargoes%20of%20Sokol%20oil%20the%20IOC%20was%20supposed%20to%20receive%20from%20late%20November%20to%20December%2C%20Reuters%20reported%2C%20citing%20shipping%20data.%20So%20the%20cargoes%20have%20mostly%20been%20lingering%20at%20sea%20around%20India%20and%20Sri%20