quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221079%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Lipstick-Face%20Demon%20in%20%26quot%3BInsidious%3A%20The%20Red%20Door.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c77b57a3c8094d5dd7f66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22608%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Lipstick-Face%20Demon%20in%20%26quot%3BInsidious%3A%20The%20Red%20Door.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Pictures%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20love%20Patrick%20Wilson's%20work%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Conjuring%26quot%3B%20franchise%2C%20and%20support%20his%20transition%20to%20directing%20wholeheartedly.%20But%20even%20though%20Wilson%20clearly%20tried%20his%20hardest%2C%20%26quot%3BInsidious%3A%20The%20Red%20Door%26quot%3B%20just%20doesn't%20cut%20it%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20did%20we%20really%20need%20another%20%26quot%3BInsidious%26quot%3B%20film%3F%20The%20franchise%20has%20had%20some%20interesting%20moments%2C%20but%20overall%2C%20the%20films%20have%20gradually%20declined%20in%20quality.%20And%20%26quot%3BInsidious%3A%20The%20Red%20Door%26quot%3B%20doesn't%20even%20dive%20deep%20into%20the%20mythology%20of%20the%20universe%2C%20including%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20Lipstick-Face%20Demon%2C%20which%20feels%20like%20a%20wasted%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20this%20final%20installment%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BInsidious%26quot%3B%20franchise%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20letdown%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20even%20%3Cem%3Ethat%3C%2Fem%3E%20scary%2C%20which%2C%20for%20a%20horror%20movie%2C%20is%20pretty%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWorst%3A%20%26quot%3BPet%20Sematary%3A%20Bloodlines%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221802%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jellybean%20the%20Australian%20Cattle%20Dog%20as%20Hedricks%20in%20%26quot%3BPet%20Sematary%3A%20Bloodlines.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657c81dd0ec98e92f74ffba5%3Fformat%3Djpe