%20name%20and%20executive%20produced%20by%20the%20Obamas%2C%20that%20program%20begins%20with%20%26quot%3Bisolation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20film%2C%20internet%20and%20cellular%20services%20are%20shut%20down%2C%20cable%20is%20cut%20off%2C%20and%20transportation%20such%20as%20oil%20tankers%2C%20airplanes%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-leave-the-world-behind-netflix-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETeslas%3C%2Fa%3E%20mysteriously%20go%20haywire%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmahershala-ali-wins-oscar-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMahershala%20Ali%3C%2Fa%3E's%20character%2C%20George%20'G.H.'%20Scott%2C%20would%20be%20to%20make%20the%20target%20nation%20%26quot%3Bas%20deaf%2C%20dumb%2C%20and%20paralyzed%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%20to%20cause%20confusion%20and%20eventually%20topple%20an%20already-divided%20country's%20government%20from%20within%20by%20sparking%20a%20civil%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECould%20hackers%20or%20a%20foreign%20adversary%20pull%20off%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-a-cyber-attack%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecyberattack%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20the%20one%20seen%20in%20%26quot%3BLeave%20the%20World%20Behind%26quot%3B%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%20proposes%20a%20chilling%20scenario%2C%20but%20it's%20highly%20unlikely%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-cyber-security%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%3C%2Fa%3E%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChad%20Heitzenrater%2C%20a%20senior%20information%20scientist%20at%20RAND%20Corporation%20specializing%20in%20cyberwarfare%20and%20a%20former%20government%20employee%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20an%20attack%20as%20sophisticated%20and%20large-scale%20as%20the%20one%20in%20the%20film%20would%20require%20nearly%20impossible%20coordination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeitzenrater%20noted%20that%20the%20views%20he%20expressed%20to%20BI%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20views%20of%20RAND.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20planning%20that%20goes%20into%20it%2C%20and%20many%20of%20these%20operations%20just%20like%20any%20military%20operation%20%E2%80%A6%20they're%20not%20guaranteed%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitzenrater%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20to%20have%20that%20many%20things%20you're%20going%20to%20act%20on%2C%20be%20%3Cem%3Ethat%3C%2Fem%3E%20assured%20they're%20all%20going%20to%20work%2C%20and%20execute%20them%20in%20a%20timeframe%20that%20makes%20them%20all%20look%20that%20coordinated%20such%20that%20everything%20is%20out%20all%20at%20once%20%E2%80%94%20that%20would%20be%20a%20really%20heavy%20lift%20for%20anybody%2C%20even%20for%20a%20nation-state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELarge-scale%20vs.%20small-scale%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETake%2C%20for%20example%2C%20how%20the%20film%20suggests%20that%20cellphone%20service%20was%20disrupted%20across%20all%20networks%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20have%20been%20cases%20when%20cell%20networks%20have%20been%20shut%20down%2C%20Heitzenrater%20said%20that%20taking%20down%20the%20entire%20network%20of%20just%20one%20provider%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fverizon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVerizon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20owns%20its%20telecommunications%20network%2C%20%26quot%3Bwould%20be%20hard%20to%20imagine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20could%20be%20some%20aspect%20of%20a%20provider%20in%20which%20a%20bad%20actor%20can%20take%20advantage%20of%20a%20vulnerability%20that%20can%20impact%20its%20entire%20network%20%E2%80%94%20in%20his%20field%20of%20work%2C%20Heitzenrater%20says%20he's%20not%20one%20to%20say%20anything%20is%20impossible%20%E2%80%94%20but%20a%20%26quot%3Bfar%20more%20likely%26quot%3B%20scenario%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20regional%20or%20limited%26quot%3B%20impact%20on%20one%20cellphone%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20goes%20for%20the%20widespread%20impact%20of%20transportation.%20In%20the%20film%2C%20the%20navigation%20systems%20of%20ships%2C%20airplanes%2C%20and%20Teslas%20are%20somehow%20overridden.%20A%20more%20plausible%20plan%20would%20be%20a%20localized%20impact%20on%20planes%20since%20air%20travel%20is%20increasingly%20automated%2C%20Heitzenrater%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJasson%20Casey%2C%20CEO%20of%20Beyond%20Identity%2C%20an%20authentication%20platform%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fnewsletters%2F2023-12-20%2Fleave-the-world-behind-could-netflix-movie-s-cyberattack-actually-happen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20hacking%20boats%20and%20planes%20and%20sending%20%26quot%3Bfake%20navigation%20signals%26quot%3B%20is%20possible%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bmost%20of%20the%20planes%20and%20boats%20still%20have%20an%20ability%20for%20the%20crew%20to%20take%20over%20if%20something%20seems%20amiss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20even%20think%20this%20would%20be%20likely%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitzenrater%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20more%20concerning%20scenario%20would%20be%20if%20someone%20were%20to%20disrupt%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration's%20computerized%20planning%20systems%2C%20in%20which%20case%20flights%20would%20have%20to%20stay%20grounded%20until%20the%20problem%20is%20solved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20cyberwarfare%20cheap%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20a%20cyberattack%20of%20this%20level%20is%20%26quot%3Bcost-effective%26quot%3B%20is%20also%20hard%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20answer%20that%20question%2C%20I%20would%20have%20one%20of%20those%20papers%20that%20everybody%20references%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitzenrater%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20operation%20of%20this%20scale%20certainly%20wouldn't%20be%20cheap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20can%20make%20a%20cyberattack%20%26quot%3Bcheap%26quot%3B%20is%20that%20vulnerabilities%20in%20a%20particular%20system%20can%20sometimes%20allow%20hackers%20to%20impact%20a%20lot%20of%20targets%2C%20and%20the%20bad%20actor%20can%20use%20that%20vulnerability%20repeatedly%2C%20he%20said.%20And%20in%20the%20case%20of%20one%20cybercriminal%20taking%20advantage%20of%20some%20vulnerability%20through%2C%20for%20example%2C%20ransomware%2C%20the%20operation%20would%20be%20fairly%20inexpensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20a%20larger%20scale%2C%20finding%20vulnerabilities%20across%20multiple%20sectors%20would%20require%20immense%20reconnaissance%20or%20intelligence%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20think%20about%20it%20in%20that%20aggregate%2C%20then%20it's%20not%20as%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20Heitzenrater%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-leave-the-world-behind-movie-cyberattack-real-life-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703631985000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658b4cf41c5c7b8c9a0c20cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-leave-the-world-behind-movie-cyberattack-real-life-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Netflix's%20new%20movie%2C%20%26quot%3BLeave%20the%20World%20Behind%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20cyberattack%20shuts%20down%20communications%20across%20the%20US.%20Experts%20say%20it's%20unlikely%20in%20real%20life.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-leave-the-world-behind-movie-cyberattack-real-life-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taraji%20P.%20Henson%20Fired%20Her%20Team%20After%20%E2%80%98Empire%E2%80%99%20Success%20Led%20Nowhere%20and%20Cookie%20Spinoff%20Fai