ic%2C%20Disney%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20has%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20claiming%20that%20the%20oversight%20government%20for%20Walt%20Disney%20World%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-desantis-signs-bill-stripping-disney-tax-district-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20appointees%20of%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20has%20failed%20to%20release%20documents%20and%20properly%20preserve%20records%20in%20violation%20of%20Florida%20public%20records%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suit%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-desantis-feud-timeline-parental-rights-education-florida-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20latest%20in%20a%20growing%20list%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20legal%20disputes%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-backed-disney-board-says-employees-2-million-back-taxes-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadministrative%20skirmishes%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20oversight%20government%20and%20the%20theme%20park%20conglomerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20said%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20filed%20Friday%20that%20the%20Central%20Florida%20Tourism%20Oversight%20District%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20CFTOD%2C%20has%20been%20so%20slow%20in%20fulfilling%20its%20public%20records%20duties%20that%20it%20has%20failed%20to%20respond%20completely%20to%20a%20request%20the%20company%20made%20seven%20months%20ago%20when%20it%20paid%20more%20than%20%242%2C400%20to%20get%20emails%20and%20text%20messages%20belonging%20to%20the%20five%20district%20board%20members%20appointed%20by%20DeSantis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%2C%20DeSantis%2C%20and%20the%20DeSantis%20appointees%20are%20already%20battling%20for%20control%20in%20two%20pending%20federal%20and%20state%20court%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20public%20records%20lawsuit%20asks%20a%20judge%20to%20review%20any%20documents%20the