-tribal-woman-burnt-alive-2645007.html%5C%22%3Epolice%20have%20arrested%20six%20individuals%3C%2Fa%3E%20believed%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20attack.%20The%20suspects%2C%20all%20residents%20of%20the%20same%20village%2C%20are%20currently%20in%20police%20custody%2C%20awaiting%20further%20legal%20proceedings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20Assam%20has%20one%20of%20the%20most%20stringent%20laws%20against%20witch-hunting%2C%20yet%20instances%20of%20women%20being%20chased%20away%20or%20killed%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20being%20witches%20still%20surface%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Assam%20government%20data%2C%20between%202011%20and%202019%2C%20107%20people%20were%20killed%20across%20the%20state%20in%20witch-hunting%20incidents%2C%20%3Cem%3EOutlook%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fwitch-hunting-the-invisible-village-in-assam-magazine-265408%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Assam%20Witch%20Hunting%20(Prohibition%2C%20Prevention%20and%20Protection)%20Act%20was%20passed%20in%202018.%20However%2C%20the%20conviction%20rates%20in%20these%20cases%20remain%20low%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703572239000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F26113836%2FScreenshot-2023-12-26-at-11.37.4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fassam-tribal-woman-killed-witchcraft%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%2C%20identified%20as%20Sangita%20Kapi%2C%20belonged%20to%20the%20Adivasi%20community%20and%20is%20survived%20by%20her%20husband%20and%20three%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fassam-tribal-woman-killed-witchcraft%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22t