hould%20replace%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%20in%20every%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintain%20the%20temperature%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGiven%20its%20geography%2C%20Sanjay%20says%20that%20Osmanabad%20has%20a%20fluctuating%20temperature%20between%2020%20and%2040%20degrees%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%2C%20we%20must%20ensure%20a%20temperature%20of%2032%20degrees%20Celsius.%20It%20should%20not%20exceed%2035%20degrees.%20We%20have%20externally%20used%20aerators%20to%20regulate%20the%20temperature%20inside%20the%20water%20bank.%20It%20also%20boosts%20fresh%20algae%20growth%20and%20provides%20new%20micronutrients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Sanjay%20Pawar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700662267000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20incurred%20huge%20losses%20because%20of%20recurring%20droughts%2C%2010%20farmers%20from%20Osmanabad%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20switched%20to%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%20to%20reap%20profits.%20One%20of%20the%20farmers%2C%20Sanjay%20Pawar%20shares%20six%20tips%20for%20beginners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334671%2Fmaharashtra-farmers-oyster-pearl-cultivation-battle-drought-suicide-earn-income%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Colours%20of%20Hope%3A%20%E2%80%98My%20Daughter%2C%20A%20Bharatnatyam%20Dancer%2C%20Was%20Told%20She%E2%80%99ll%20Never%20Walk%20Nor%20Hear%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUjjwala%20Sahane%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20excited%20to%20start%20their%20family%20in%201985%20when%20they%20